<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jiǎo qián yǒu dēng 迦南1217</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jiǎo qián yǒu dēng lù shàng yǒu guāng, yé sū cháng zài nǐ shēn páng.
 bù yào jù pà bù yào jīng huāng, zhǔ huì shí jiā lì liàng.
 suī yǒu běi fēng yī rán shǒu wàng, yún mǎn zhèng shì zhǔ ēn pèi jiàng.
 nǐ shì mài zi nǐ shì dēng tái, yào jié zi lì yào fā guāng.
 la la la la la la la la, jiǎo qián yǒu dēng lù shàng yǒu guāng.
 yé sū ài wǒ yé sū ài nǐ, yǒng yuǎn bǎ nǐ wǒ jì xīn shàng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1217</hymn_number>
</song>